headline: 5 Insightful Analyst Questions From Starbucks’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Starbucks’ results for Q4 were met with a positive market reaction, as the company delivered sales growth above Wall Street’s expectations but reported non-GAAP earnings per share below consensus.
